<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.10.5">
<l>iliṅkat tiṭṭa purāṇat tīruñ camaṇaruñ cākkiyarum</l>
<l>valintu vātucey vīrkaḷu maṟṟunun teyvamu mākiniṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>malintu cennel kavari vīcun tirukkuru kūrataṉuḷ</l>
<l>polintu niṉṟapi rāṉkaṇṭī roṉṟum poyyillai pōṟṟumiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You from the purāṇas based on the linga and you who forecefull hold dispute</l>
<l>with Jaina devotees and Buddha devotees, he stands as your god too.</l>
<l>See the lord who prosperously stands in Tirukkurukūr where they abundantly</l> 
<l>wave fans of red paddy. There is not one lie. Praise [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
